#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.204"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.204:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.204:0.2"
msgid "21. Sappurisavagga"
msgstr "21. A Good Person"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: catutthasappurisasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.204:0.3"
msgid "204. Dasakammasutta"
msgstr "204. Ten Kinds of Deeds"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.220"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.204:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Asappurisañca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi, asappurisena asappurisatarañca;"
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you a bad person and a worse person,"

msgctxt "an4.204:1.2"
msgid "sappurisañca, sappurisena sappurisatarañca. Taṃ suṇātha … pe …."
msgstr "a good person and a better person."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.204:2.1"
msgid "“Katamo ca, bhikkhave, asappuriso?"
msgstr "And what is a bad person?"

msgctxt "an4.204:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco pāṇātipātī hoti, adinnādāyī hoti, kāmesumicchācārī "
"hoti, musāvādī hoti, pisuṇavāco hoti, pharusavāco hoti, samphappalāpī hoti, "
"abhijjhālu hoti, byāpannacitto hoti, micchādiṭṭhiko hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s someone who kills living creatures, steals, and commits sexual "
"misconduct. They use speech that’s false, divisive, harsh, or nonsensical. "
"And they’re covetous, malicious, with wrong view."

msgctxt "an4.204:2.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asappuriso."
msgstr "This is called a bad person."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.204:3.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, asappurisena asappurisataro?"
msgstr "And what is a worse person?"

msgctxt "an4.204:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco attanā ca pāṇātipātī hoti, parañca pāṇātipāte "
"samādapeti … pe … attanā ca abhijjhālu hoti, parañca abhijjhāya samādapeti;"
msgstr ""
"It’s someone who kills living creatures, steals, and commits sexual "
"misconduct. They use speech that’s false, divisive, harsh, or nonsensical. "
"They’re covetous, malicious, with wrong view. And they encourage others to "
"do these things."

msgctxt "an4.204:3.3"
msgid ""
"attanā ca byāpannacitto hoti, parañca byāpāde samādapeti, attanā ca "
"micchādiṭṭhiko hoti, parañca micchādiṭṭhiyā samādapeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.204:3.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asappurisena asappurisataro."
msgstr "This is called a worse person."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.204:4.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, sappuriso?"
msgstr "And what is a good person?"

msgctxt "an4.204:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti … pe … anabhijjhālu hoti, "
"abyāpannacitto hoti, sammādiṭṭhiko hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s someone who doesn’t kill living creatures, steal, or commit sexual "
"misconduct. They don’t use speech that’s false, divisive, harsh, or "
"nonsensical. And they’re contented, kind-hearted, with right view."

msgctxt "an4.204:4.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sappuriso."
msgstr "This is called a good person."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.204:5.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, sappurisena sappurisataro?"
msgstr "And what is a better person?"

msgctxt "an4.204:5.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco attanā ca pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti, parañca "
"pāṇātipātā veramaṇiyā samādapeti … pe … attanā ca anabhijjhālu hoti, parañca "
"anabhijjhāya samādapeti;"
msgstr ""
"It’s someone who doesn’t kill living creatures, steal, or commit sexual "
"misconduct. They don’t use speech that’s false, divisive, harsh, or "
"nonsensical. They’re contented, kind-hearted, with right view. And they "
"encourage others to do these things."

msgctxt "an4.204:5.3"
msgid "attanā ca abyāpannacitto hoti, parañca abyāpāde samādapeti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.204:5.4"
msgid "attanā ca sammādiṭṭhiko hoti, parañca sammādiṭṭhiyā samādapeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.204:5.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sappurisena sappurisataro”ti."
msgstr "This is called a better person.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.204:5.6"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
